name: Process Texture 102
description: A beautiful, glitchy, abstract texture I created as a layer for My current work in progress (WIP). A dark, bruise-colored, abstract piece with overlapping rectilinear forms. The image shifts from near-black on the left edge to the right through colors and edges, revealing streaks and smears of magenta, blue, and purple against a background of light grey. A Rothko shuffle of chthonian cards. 2000x2700 pixels. Only 0.17 tez. 17% royalty rate. Minted June 19th, 2021.
